com.github.misberner.apcommons.util.methods

Enum ObjectMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ObjectMethod>
      • com.github.misberner.apcommons.util.methods.ObjectMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ObjectMethod>

    public enum ObjectMethod
extends Enum<ObjectMethod>
    Enumeration class to refer to methods defined by Object in a static manner. The values of this enum correspond to the following methods:
    • Object.clone()
    • Object.finalize()
    • Object.getClass()
    • Object.hashCode()
    • Object.notify()
    • Object.notifyAll()
    • Object.toString()
    • Object.wait()
    • Object.equals(Object)
    • Object.wait(long)
    • Object.wait(long, int)
    Author:
    Malte Isberner
